an><hr size=1> The two of you should definetly be able to get the heart of frost in perma. <br>
Here is what I did...<br>
<br>
Invis up at the zone and run in to the flag room (room #3 on this map) <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.eqatlas.com/permafrostmap.html">www.eqatlas.com/permafrostmap.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <br>
<br>
Facing into the room, move to the right hand corner of the room, hugging the wall. Don't go down the ramp you come to, just stay on the top ledge.<br>
<br>
Kill everything on the top ledge, and anything else you think you can manage (the goblin elite guards can be a handfull at your level, but I bet you could do them).<br>
<br>
Goblin Wizards *definetly* spawn in this area on a decent basis, especially I found, in the right hand corner near the ramp down to where the king is.<br>
<br>
If you are careful enough, you can solo this room. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=eardar>Eardar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/24/02 2:55 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF</span><hr size=1> Thanks everyone for your help, I just completed the quest tonight. Me and my shaman friend did it all by ourselves. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://houseofeq.d2g.com/earsig2.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=656.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=656.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=656.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.threadControl?topicID=656.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=656.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=htt